k incomplete. For instance I cannot see any conversation between AsurNZ (or=
 any assessor) and Tower and any notes in that regard. Could you please pro=
vide those ASAP?

Thank you for sharing the initial information

I had a quick scan and it look incomplete. For instance I cannot see any co=
nversation between AsurNZ (or any assessor) and Tower and any notes in that=
 regard. Could you please provide those ASAP?

Thanks and regards,
Raffaella



